    public abstract class AddrAttr
extends StunAttr
    Superclass for attributes carrying IPv4 address and ports. Quantities in the value byte array are construed as big-endian unsigned integers. Bytewise: +-----+-----+----+----+ | 0 | 1 | port | +-----+-----+----+----+ | IPv4 address | +-----+-----+----+----+
    Author:
    Jim Dixon
